HT32F5xxxx Standard Peripheral Firmware Library

HT32F5xxxx Standard Peripheral Firmware Library is a software package that contains routines, Macros, Data Types, Structure Types, Functions and Examples of HT32F5xxxx peripherals. This complete package can be used on HT32F5xxxx series.

To use this Firmware Library, advanced knowledge about HT32F5xxxx's peripherals specification is not required and thus reduce much development cost.

HT32F5xxxx Standard Peripheral Firmware Library is also CMSIS-compliant.
